1939;;Heroes in Blue;;American;;William Watson;;Dick Purcell, Bernadene Hayes;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes_in_Blue;;Moran, a gangster, hires Joe Murphy to make a large wager on a horse race. The horse wins, but Joe steals the mob's payoff.<br><br>Joe's policeman brother, Terry, becomes involved after the gangsters threaten their father, Mike. He has to go after his brother to get the money back, while also making sure Moran ends up behind bars.